**Thesis:** Most people see a "hot internet girl" famous for being *looked at* — Kanye's muse, the "Uncah Jams" meme, vibes with no thoughts. Through Enneagram Type 4, Julia Fox has spent her life turning the experience of being discarded into art she signs. She was never the muse; she held the brush.

**Core tension:** object vs. author. **Signature detail anchor:** the 2017 *R.I.P. Julia Fox* show — silk canvases painted in her own blood, staged before fame. **Emotional thesis:** a child left alone in an empty apartment learned she was disposable and spent her life becoming the one thing no one could throw away.

